<template>
  <el-form style="margin: 10px 0 0 25px">
    <el-row justify="center" type="flex">
      <el-col>
        <el-form-item :label="$t('pdtempPdAcc.pdacc')">
          <el-tag type="info">{{account.pdAccCode+':'+account.pdAccName}}</el-tag>
        </el-form-item>
      </el-col>
      <el-col>
        <el-form-item :label="$t('pdtempPdAcc.accounttype')">
          <el-tag type="info">{{account.pdAccountType | filter_accountType}}</el-tag>
        </el-form-item>
      </el-col>
    </el-row>
  </el-form>
</template>
<script>
  import MyVue from "@/main"

  export default {
    name: "accountInfo",
    props: {
      account: {
        type: Object,
        required: true
      }
    },
    filters: {
      filter_accountType(code) {
        return MyVue.getCodeName('accountTypeAll', code)
      }
    },
    data() {
      return {}
    },
    created() {
    }
  }
</script>
